<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Africa Journal</title>
  <style>
    /* Base styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #171717, #2d2d2d);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .logo {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      border-left: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      border-right: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #ef4444;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .divider {
      border-top: 3px solid #22c55e;
      margin: 10px 0;
      width: 50px;
    }
    .accent {
      color: #22c55e;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">Africa Journal</span><br>
        <span style="font-size: 16px;">of Social Work and Social Policy</span>
      </div>
      <div class="divider" style="margin: 15px auto;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome, {{name}}!</h2>
      
      <p>Thank you for registering with the Africa Journal of Social Work and Social Policy. We're excited to have you join our community as a <strong>{{role}}</strong>.</p>
      
      <p>The Africa Journal promotes Indigenous African knowledge systems and decolonial social work methodologies through scholarly research and community engagement. Your participation will help advance these important goals.</p>
      
      <h3>What's Next?</h3>
      
      <p>You can now access our platform to:</p>
      <ul>
        {{#if_eq role "author"}}
          <li>Submit your manuscripts</li>
          <li>Track the review process</li>
          <li>Respond to reviewer feedback</li>
        {{/if_eq}}
        
        {{#if_eq role "reviewer"}}
          <li>Review assigned manuscripts</li>
          <li>Submit your evaluations</li>
          <li>Contribute to scholarly discourse</li>
        {{/if_eq}}
        
        {{#if_eq role "editor"}}
          <li>Manage submissions</li>
          <li>Assign reviewers</li>
          <li>Make editorial decisions</li>
        {{/if_eq}}
        
        {{#if_eq role "admin"}}
          <li>Manage user accounts</li>
          <li>Oversee editorial processes</li>
          <li>Publish accepted articles</li>
        {{/if_eq}}
      </ul>
      
      <p>We recommend completing your profile with your research interests and affiliations to help us match you with relevant content.</p>
      
      <a href="https://africajournal.org/login" class="button">Sign In Now</a>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to <a href="https://africajournal.org/contact" style="color: #22c55e; text-decoration: none;">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{current_year}} Africa Journal of Social Work and Social Policy</p>
      <p>East Africa Social Work Regional Resource Centre</p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://africajournal.org/privacy" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="https://africajournal.org/unsubscribe" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">Unsubscribe</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
